Dialog Mission Statement This is the dialog for Vandar Tokare, a member of the Jedi Council.
The first dialog is a scripted one when the player first shares a dream with Bastila after being considered for Jedi training. The second dialog is the first time the player talks to him after saving Juhani. The third dialog is the first time the player talks to him after having killed Juhani. The fourth dialog is his response to the player having discovered the Star Map before the Council assigned the quest. The fifth dialog is subsequent conversations before the player has become a Padawan. The sixth dialog is the first time the player talks to him after becoming a Padawan. The seventh dialog is subsequent conversation during the Sandral-Matale romance plot. The eighth dialog is the first time the player talks to him after returning Shen to his father. The ninth dialog is the first time the player talks to him after Shen and Rahasia run away to the Jedi Enclave. The tenth dialog is the firt time the player talks to him after Nurik accepts Shen and Rahasia. The eleventh dialog is a scripted conversation when the player comes back from finding the Star Map after becoming a Padawan. The twelfth dialog is the first time the player talks to him after being given the main quest. The thirteenth dialog is subsequent times the player talks to him after being given the main quest.
Exit points in conversation:
Exit stream 1: The lines are said and the conversation ends. The player has the possibility of 3 minor dark side hits if they lie or are arrogant. DAN_JEDI_PLOT is set to 2 to show that the player has been accepted for Jedi training.
Exit stream 2: The line is said and the conversation ends. DAN_VANDARJ_DONE is set to TRUE to show that this conversation has taken place.
Exit stream 3: The lines are said and the conversation ends. DAN_VANDARJ_DONE is set to TRUE to show that this conversation has taken place.

Exit stream 10: The lines are said and the conversation ends. DAN_VANDARS_DONE is set to TRUE to show that this conversation has taken place.
Exit stream 11: The lines are said and no matter what the player chooses, Vandar gives them the main quest. DAN_PLANET_PLOT is set to 2 to show that the main quest has been given. DAN_VANDARR_DONE is set to TRUE to show that Vandar has talked to them about what they found in the ruins.
Exit stream 12: The lines are said and the conversation ends. DAN_VANDARP_DONE is set to TRUE to show that this conversation has taken place.
